Description: Calculates the slope (longitudinal gradient or steepness)
  of linear geographic features such as roads <doi:10.1038/s41597-019-0147-x>
  and rivers <doi:10.1016/j.jhydrol.2018.06.066>. It can use local
  Digital Elevation Model (DEM) data or download DEM data via the 'ceramic'
  package. The package also provides functions to add elevation data to
  linestrings and visualize elevation profiles.
